1. *Ortak* mi je poslao mejl.(My partner sent me an email.)
 
2. Pratili smo *ortaka* u trgovini.(We followed our partner to the store.)

3. Nalazimo se sa *ortakom* svakog četvrtka.(We meet with our partner every Thursday.)

4. Nismo znali da će *ortaci* biti na partiju.(We didn't know that our partners were going to be at the party.)

5. Pronašli smo novog *ortaka* za naš projekat.(We found a new partner for our project.)